==English==
===Alternative forms===
* {{l|en|japie}}
===Etymology===
From {{uder|en|af|japie}}, short for {{m|af|plaasjapie||farm-boy}}, referring to any person who grew up on a farm and is unfamiliar with city life, and hence naive and unsophisticated.
